      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full-length wedding portrait. The bride is seated, wearing a wedding dress. Her bridal bouquet has been placed on a ćilim (woven tapestry-like rug) at her feet. She is leaning against the groom, who is standing next to her, dressed in a white dress shirt, a bow tie and a black suit with a sprig of rosemary on the lapel. He is holding a hat in his left hand. They have been photographed in front of a painted canvas backdrop depicting a fireplace.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">On the verso the names of the couple in the photograph as well as their kinship relation to the owner of the picture are noted.</ab>
